information we collect and hold includes information about the end users our applications and individuals who visit our website.
The personal information that we collect and hold may include an individual's:
· name;
· address;
· date of birth;
· email address;
· telephone number and other contact details;
· workplace; and
· technical data, which may include IP address, the types of devices you are using to access the website, device attributes, browser type, language and operating system.
